  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nCurrently we abuse selectively emiting \"unknownBlockRoot\" in the block pool to suppress backwards sync. This is confusing, since the block pool should not be concerned with syncing strategy. There might also be eventually other consumers of \"unknownBlockRoot\" which need every unknown block root to fire an event.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nSync controls backwards sync.\r\n\r\n**Screenshots**\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/master/packages/lodestar/src/chain/blocks/pool.ts#L35",
